summary: TL* THE CONTACT OWNS 2008 JEEP LIBERTY LIMITED EDITION. THE CONTACT STATED THAT WATER WAS LEAKING INTO THE VEHICLE FROM THE CEILING ABOVE THE DOME LIGHT AREA. ADDITIONALLY, WATER WOULD LEAK INTO THE TRUNK. THE FAILURE WOULD OCCUR WHENEVER IT WOULD RAIN. THE VEHICLE WAS NOT TAKEN TO THE DEALER FOR INSPECTION OR REPAIRS. THE MANUFACTURER WAS MADE AWARE OF THE FAILURE.  THE FAILURE MILEAGE WAS 66,000.
